{"type":"message","id":"61b828f2","parentId":"97cc11d8","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:17:46.515Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有找到之前生成的CSV文件。让我尝试另一种方法，快速获取一些股票的实时行情信息作为推送内容。我可以使用 akshare 获取大盘指数和一些热门股票的基本情况。\n\n现在让我编写一个简化的脚本来快速获取当前市场情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没有历史结果。现在已过交易时间，让我快速获取大盘和热门股票的基本情况："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0790e8a27096439b8b66fa68","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\quant-stocks\\quick_analysis.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n快速股票分析 - 非交易时段简化版\n\"\"\"\n\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"【市场快报】\")\nprint(f\"时间: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint()\n\n# 1. 获取主要指数\nprint(\"📊 主要指数：\")\ntry:\n    indices = ak.stock_zh_index_spot_em()\n    main_indices = indices[indices['代码'].isin(['000001', '399001', '399006'])]\n    for _, row in main_indices.iterrows():\n        change_pct = float(row['涨跌幅'])\n        symbol = \"📈\" if change_pct > 0 else \"📉\"\n        print(f\"  {symbol} {row['名称']}: {row['最新价']} ({change_pct:+.2f}%)\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  获取指数失败: {e}\")\nprint()\n\n# 2. 获取涨停板股票（表现强势）\nprint(\"🔥 今日涨停板（前10）：\")\ntry:\n    limit_up = ak.stock_zt_pool_em(date=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d'))\n    if len(limit_up) > 0:\n        for i, (_, row) in enumerate(limit_up.head(10).iterrows(), 1):\n            print(f\"  {i}. {row['代码']} {row['名称']} ({row['最新价']})\")\n    else:\n        print(\"  今日无涨停股票\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  获取涨停板失败: {e}\")\nprint()\n\n# 3. 获取高分红股票（基本面好）\nprint(\"💰 高分红股票（股息率>5%，前10）：\")\ntry:\n    stock_list = ak.stock_zh_a_spot_em()\n    stock_list = stock_list[\n        (stock_list['代码'].str.startswith(('60', '00'))) &\n        (~stock_list['名称'].str.contains('ST'))\n    ]\n\n    # 获取股息率\n    dividend_data = ak.stock_dividend_detail_em()\n    if not dividend_data.empty:\n        latest_dividend = dividend_data.groupby('股票代码')['每10股派息数'].sum().reset_index()\n        latest_dividend.columns = ['代码', '年度分红(元/10股)']\n\n        stock_list = stock_list.merge(latest_dividend, on='代码', how='left')\n        stock_list['股息率(%)'] = (stock_list['年度分红(元/10股)'] / 10 / stock_list['最新价']) * 100\n\n        high_dividend = stock_list[\n            (stock_list['股息率(%)'] > 5) &\n            (stock_list['股息率(%)'] < 20)  # 排除异常值\n        ].sort_values('股息率(%)', ascending=False).head(10)\n\n        for i, (_, row) in enumerate(high_dividend.iterrows(), 1):\n            print(f\"  {i}. {row['代码']} {row['名称']} 股息率: {row['股息率(%)']:.2f}% PE: {row['市盈率-动态']:.2f}\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  获取高分红股票失败: {e}\")\nprint()\n\n# 4. 资金流向\nprint(\"💵 主力资金净流入（前10）：\")\ntry:\n    money_flow = ak.stock_individual_fund_flow_rank()\n    for i, (_, row) in enumerate(money_flow.head(10).iterrows(), 1):\n        print(f\"  {i}. {row['代码']} {row['名称']} 净流入: {row['今日主力净流入-净额']}\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  获取资金流向失败: {e}\")\nprint()\n\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"⚠️  温馨提示：\")\nprint(\"1. 当前非交易时段，数据为收盘后更新\")\nprint(\"2. 仅供参考，不构成投资建议\")\nprint(\"3. 投资有风险，入市需谨慎\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":220,"output":1081,"cacheRead":20926,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22227,"cost":{"input":0.00013199999999999998,"output":0.0023782,"cacheRead":0.00230186,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00481206}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774858605447}}
