{"type":"message","id":"05a3d2da","parentId":"0ffcb352","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:20:02.037Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"脚本又因为网络请求问题而失败了。看起来 akshare 的数据源在非交易时段可能不稳定，或者网络请求超时。\n\n不过，我已经获得了一些有用的信息：\n- 上证指数: 3923.29 (+0.24%)\n- 今日涨停板前10名\n\n让我基于这些信息整理一个推送内容，并说明完整分析在交易时间内会更准确。\n\n让我再尝试一个更简化的版本，只获取大盘指数和几个关键信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"数据获取不稳定。让我用最简化的方式获取基本信息："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dd9508cca7c74d539aa3c388","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\quant-stocks\\simple_analysis.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n简化版股票快报 - 非交易时段\n\"\"\"\n\nimport akshare as ak\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport sys\nimport io\n\nif sys.platform == 'win32':\n    sys.stdout = io.TextIOWrapper(sys.stdout.buffer, encoding='utf-8', errors='replace')\n\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"【股市快报】\")\nprint(f\"时间: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint()\n\n# 1. 获取主要指数\nprint(\"【主要指数】\")\ntry:\n    indices = ak.stock_zh_index_spot_em()\n    main_indices = indices[indices['代码'].isin(['000001', '399001', '399006', '000688'])]\n    for _, row in main_indices.iterrows():\n        change_pct = float(row['涨跌幅'])\n        trend = \"↑\" if change_pct > 0 else \"↓\"\n        print(f\"  {row['名称']}: {row['最新价']} ({trend}{abs(change_pct):.2f}%)\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  获取指数失败: {e}\")\nprint()\n\n# 2. 获取市场概况\nprint(\"【市场概况】\")\ntry:\n    stock_list = ak.stock_zh_a_spot_em()\n    # 排除ST股\n    stock_list = stock_list[~stock_list['名称'].str.contains('ST')]\n\n    total = len(stock_list)\n    up_count = len(stock_list[stock_list['涨跌幅'] > 0])\n    down_count = len(stock_list[stock_list['涨跌幅'] < 0])\n    flat_count = len(stock_list[stock_list['涨跌幅'] == 0])\n    limit_up = len(stock_list[stock_list['涨跌幅'] >= 9.9])\n    limit_down = len(stock_list[stock_list['涨跌幅'] <= -9.9])\n\n    print(f\"  上涨: {up_count} 家\")\n    print(f\"  下跌: {down_count} 家\")\n    print(f\"  平盘: {flat_count} 家\")\n    print(f\"  涨停: {limit_up} 家\")\n    print(f\"  跌停: {limit_down} 家\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"  获取市场概况失败: {e}\")\nprint()\n\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(\"【温馨提示】\")\nprint(\"当前为非交易时段，数据为收盘后更新\")\nprint(\"完整量化分析建议在交易时间运行\")\nprint(\"投资有风险，入市需谨慎\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":574,"output":820,"cacheRead":23215,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24609,"cost":{"input":0.00034439999999999997,"output":0.001804,"cacheRead":0.00255365,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00470205}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774858770243}}
